{"tid":1800261,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"航空公司Online Check-in 國籍冇得揀香港係正常？","createTime":"2019-12-27T15:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T12:14:25.000Z","uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6f3a9b92d88b6e836cc565075a617e2f7cca661c","tid":1800261,"uid":245286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"話說同朋友揀咗搭大韓航空去韓國，登入咗Online Check-in打算揀位，但佢需要我哋先打資料。<br />\n<br />\n喺揀國籍呢個位，拉上拉落都搵唔到Hong Kong，用埋搜尋條bar打H係冇Hong Kong 出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起初以為係自己問題，就叫朋友試，佢用app都係搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再問咗喺今年唔同時間都有搭過呢間嘅朋友，話之前都重有得揀香港做國籍<br />\n<br />\n想問下，呢個情況係咪正常？<br />\n或者有冇巴絲喺其他航空公司都試過呢個情況？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZANy0Oa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZANy0Oa.png&h=94a003bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02a5905308d2ba4a6ec74a64c663bc30a963a608","tid":1800261,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"韓狗航空<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影衰晒韓國手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35dbae57ece86c9eef4e3ac1a90e2d70be7eccc5","tid":1800261,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:43:24.000Z","msg":"慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db657a859a1b26b6ea28c2eb68b6cdc993c4b38","tid":1800261,"uid":176834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T16:19:04.000Z","msg":"有d航空公司係咁<br />\n認命做住中國人先<br />\n光復咗就有得你揀hk架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd21f4651b5c1b69ad2b1f5b39e7d207d4f6d5be","tid":1800261,"uid":279320,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"02a5905308d2ba4a6ec74a64c663bc30a963a608","tid":1800261,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T15:41:58.000Z","msg